caption:
The #OnePlusWatch3 launches today and it’s packed full of highly accurate monitoring technology - including industry leading battery life, new health monitoring with a quick 60S Health Check-in, enhanced fitness tracking in an all new titanium, stainless steel and sapphire crystal design.

To dive into everything this incredible device has to offer, I’ve sat down with three outstanding guests:

Dr. Zijing Zeng, OnePlus Spokesperson and Head of Health Lab
Dr. Sophie Bostock, a renowned sleep expert who’ll help us understand how the watch can improve our rest and recovery.
And, last but not least, British boxing legend David Haye, here to show us how this smartwatch supports peak performance.

Check out the @OnePlus_Europe channel now for the full length video to see what this device can do.

Please visit oneplus.com for full information about pricing, availability and features disclaimers.
